lead_paragraph: Australia paceman Peter Siddle has been ruled out of the second test against South Africa in Hobart with a lower back injury, Cricket Australia said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Australia Paceman Siddle Ruled Out of Second S.Africa Test
